seller.description: Hello! My name is Reda Naji. I have been working as a Graphics Designer since 2016. I'm an expert on Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator and After Effects. I love to design and focus on full customer satisfaction through my work within the delivery time. I am very friendly and easy to communicate with. So if you have any queries or questions please feel free to contact me anytime.

reviews.comment: At first there was not much communication from redanajl. I gave him very straight forward and clear instructions. The result of the first delivery was pretty much a copy of the reference I gave him and none of the request I asked for were there. The color scheme was not what I asked and the wording was not completely there. He did apologize and said he forgot because of all the messages he was replying too. which is understandable but there was only my order and one other in his queue at the time. I asked for a revision and he did do it and the result was geared way more towards what I asked. I had to deduct some stars because of this issue. In the end he did deliver a pleasing design.

This will definitely help me grow my youtube channel with some more visual appeal. I feel like there could have been a little more creativity with how the photos were used but this was still very good! Thanks!
